        ['Finance — AML & Regulatory','<ul><li><strong>AML/CFT framework (SARLAFT):</strong> Customer due diligence (KYC), transaction monitoring, suspicious activity reporting.</li><li><strong>Operational Risk (SARO):</strong> Identification, measurement, control and monitoring of operational risk.</li><li><strong>IFRS accounting standards:</strong> Implemented in the ERP financial module.</li></ul>'],
        ['Manufacturing — Quality & Safety','<ul><li><strong>ISO 9001:</strong> Quality management system — reproducible processes, production traceability, continuous improvement.</li><li><strong>Workplace safety (SGSST):</strong> Mandatory for all Colombian employers. Implemented in the HR module.</li></ul>'],
